<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">You don't have to die before 52 if your Charm and Root break at the same time.  Use a Color Shift-style stun, mez your old pet first (important since it is hasted and dual wielding), and then root or mez the original target (root if DoTed -- a bad idea -- or mez if not DoTed).
<br />

<br />
Having both Color Shift and Color Skew up is not a bad idea if you can spare the spell slots.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
